{"type": "article", "id": 59401, "title": "袁弘张歆艺夫妇成为 H&M 新年系列代言人，OPPO R17 Pro 推出新年版 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-12-18T05:52:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5503, "name": "新年"}, {"id": 10841, "name": "HM"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181218121750uIti04BH3modpMcv.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"XigQ\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4318488115641862?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>袁弘和张歆艺夫妇成为 H&amp;M 2019 中国新年系列代言人。</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120455zxo8ZJ9veEpfWcXO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是联名</h3><p line=\"aFod\">天猫国潮行动和上海美术电影制片厂、Balabala 等童装品牌合作推出经典动画 IP <a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4318205109860469?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“大闹天宫”系列</b></a>，于今日零点开始限量发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120520lUi2YNrsQkGjD1p9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.776812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120521jD9TBuPoQ8nLOq6l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.776812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812181205225QjuVyTPfYUtK3ci.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.776812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120521yA3ktFEBbNSepKx1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.781159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的Case</h3><p line=\"S5Tc\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4318517103146120?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雷佳音今日担任支付宝会员体验官</b></a>，花名“阿拉雷”。今日支付宝会员频道全面升级，更名为“支付宝会员”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120542SVvyd3eKgmEOUQNq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812181205442COpRu4J1kAb9c6f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"YhBa\"><b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4318296293701289?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">OPPO 昨天发布了一支 OPPO R17 Pro 新年版的广告片</a>，</b>经典的众神形象加入了现代元素，来宣布新款产品于昨日开启预售。当晚代言人李易峰参加了品牌方举办的“OPPO 奇幻新年大秀”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k08142n3m11\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"orxY\"><a href=\"http://static.adcode.cn/20181210-zhihu-300/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>知乎发布 2018 年度 300 问，</b></a>知乎从今年新创建的 940 万个问题中，综合合阅读量和回答数等数据选出了最终的 300 个。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120644mITx9JVkUtyeOQhB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120644Xhiz8jZFep7uCO6D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120644dPUArV0HTv2nmCsK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"7Mz8\">潘婷联合 Vice 拍摄了一部主题为<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4318155671668530?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>\"从头定格美\"</b></a>的广告片，选择几位即将更换身份证的女性为主角，来突出头发是第二张脸的理念，证件照未必就是噩梦。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=f0813l7eu1d\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"VChe\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4317545160861022?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>YSL “美妆快闪酒店”最近登陆上海，</b></a>现场有美妆图书馆、美妆套房等 6 间主题房，每个活动日都有不同的主题之夜活动。活动从 12 月 14 日至 12 月 20 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120824vmqF9R6Pb8WVZedU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.780469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120824sXKwmbETjnlki70r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181218120824o8wxaQplBhP5Kv9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.585185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"Pscb\"><b><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/12/17/tiktok-launches-first-major-uk-marketing-campaign\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">抖音海外版 Tik Tok 推出首个英国 campaign</a>。</b>这项活动聚焦在圣诞主题上，广告片通过动感的节奏展现，如何用 App 上的创意工具拍出圣诞短视频。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s0814lipyvj\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"11AJ\"><b>Saatchi &amp; Saatchi 获得西门子家电全球广告业务</b>，团队将负责西门子家电的品牌广告策略和创意发展等传播业务。</p><p line=\"vrTH\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/wunderman-thompson-wins-crm-duties-for-carnival-cruise-line/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>伟门获得嘉年华游轮的 CRM（customer-relationship-management“客户关系管理”）业务，</b></a>还会和博主合作，将会涉及各种媒介和渠道，并且分析和研究消费者的偏好画像。</p><p line=\"vrTH\" class=\"\"><br></p><p line=\"vrTH\" class=\"\">题图来自：Unsplash@<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/lwnAz-uauDc?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matt Popovich</a></p>"}